  "response": "As of the latest recommendations and reviews, some of the best earphones under \u20b92000 in India include:\n\n1. **Realme Buds Wireless 2 Neo**: These wireless earphones offer good sound quality, a comfortable fit, and long battery life. They also support fast charging.\n\n2. **OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z**: Known for their robust build, good sound quality, and excellent battery life, these wireless earphones are a popular choice.\n\n3. **boAt Rockerz 255 Pro**: These earphones provide good bass, clear sound quality, and are comfortable to wear for long periods.\n\n4. **Sony MDR-EX150AP**: These wired earphones offer excellent sound quality and a comfortable fit. They also come with an in-line microphone for calling.\n\n5. **JBL Endurance Run**: These wired earphones deliver good sound quality, a comfortable fit, and are sweat-resistant, making them suitable for workouts.\n\n6. **Sennheiser CX 80S**: Known for their balanced sound quality and comfortable fit, these wired earphones are a great choice for music lovers.\n\nThe best choice depends on your specific needs, such as whether you prefer wired or wireless earphones, sound quality preferences, and additional features like water resistance or battery life.",
